1. U ovim *okolnostima* moramo biti oprezni. (In these circumstances, we must be cautious.)
2. Oni su uspeli da prežive uprkos teškim *okolnostima*. (They managed to survive despite difficult circumstances.)
3. *Okolnosti* su se promenile i sada je vreme za novu strategiju. (The circumstances have changed and now is the time for a new strategy.)
4. Nije bilo lako, ali su se suočili sa *okolnostima* i uspeli. (It wasn't easy, but they faced the circumstances and succeeded.)
5. Njihova sposobnost da se prilagode različitim *okolnostima* ih čini izuzetno uspešnima. (Their ability to adapt to different circumstances makes them exceptionally successful.)
6. Uzimajući u obzir sve *okolnosti*, mislim da je najbolje da odustanemo. (Considering all the circumstances, I think it's best for us to give up.)
7. Mnoge kompanije su se suočile sa teškim *okolnostima* tokom pandemije. (Many companies have faced difficult circumstances during the pandemic.)
8. Uz malo sreće, mogli bismo iskoristiti ove *okolnosti* da poboljšamo našu situaciju. (With a bit of luck, we could use these circumstances to improve our situation.)
9. Bez obzira na *okolnosti*, ne smemo odustati. (Regardless of the circumstances, we must not give up.)
10. Ponekad *okolnosti* mogu biti izvan naše kontrole. (Sometimes circumstances can be beyond our control.)